name: I'm just vibing.
description:
I don't feel comfortable watching how we are fighting each other, how we try to be someone that we are not just bc money. I have 7 months on the NFT space, is nothing of course, but sometimes I feel so lost between the original concept of community and what we are now. We can change a lot of things, but I think we don't try enough, and, of course, I'm part of the problem too.

Created by Ego Rangel 2021. From the series Fake Paintings
